{"tid":1821811,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[偽黃死全家] FB page”中女講呢啲”扮黃","createTime":"2020-01-12T14:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T03:09:46.000Z","uid":304872,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff58250928004d9d23020f7b55d55a5c0563d6f","tid":1821811,"uid":304872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:22:38.000Z","msg":"事源樓豬唔記得幾時like埋啲咁嘅垃圾page <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁啱見到呢個「中女講呢啲」出埋啲cctvb台慶post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都好奇怪<br />\n因為印象中佢都係黃page<br />\n點會出啲咁嘅post<br />\n所以即管入去睇下啲留言到 <br />\n再入去屌下班港豬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點撚知 即時被人del cm加block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你藍你港豬睇cctvb無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但share埋啲抗爭post扮黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又出post幫cctvb宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解咁嘅偽黃page都可以有80k likes? <br />\n幫手入去屌鳩佢再unlike啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/606915276074309/posts/2539461039486380?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F606915276074309%2Fposts%2F2539461039486380%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=d764b4de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/606915276074309/posts/2539461039486380?sfns=mo</a><br />\n唔可以俾呢啲垃圾偽黃page生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uhTwGHt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuhTwGHt.png&h=cb4d6c72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqqZQAS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaqqZQAS.png&h=3ffb31b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i